channel.title: [CLOSED Project OblivionX |A server development | 459 server [CLOSED]
channel.description:
Project OblivionX
- About the project - This is a server who will look "kinda" like RS 07/08, we are not saying that this project will be a server who is 100% like Runescape in 2007/2008, just the good old game, which you can play without the newer stuff, there will be two versions: 317 and 459. If you have an account in the 317 version your account will have the exact same stuff as you have in the 459 version and your account will also be saved in both the versions I hope people wanna support us in the progress of creating Project OblivionX. The server is Project Insanity based.
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/40y8x.png[/img]
[size=18pt]The server now runs by no-ip :) we will soon release a pre-alpha version :)[/size]
The red color code means the feature has not yet been started. The orange color code means the feature has been started and is under construction. The green color code means the feature has been finished.
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/qnoi69.jpg[/img] [b]Combat[/b] •Won't start working on until all non-combat skills are finished. [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/25tgmrd.png[/img] [b]Magic[/b] •Won't start working on until all non-combat skills are finished. [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/spydf4.png[/img] [b]Ranged[/b] •Won't start working on until all non-combat skills are finished. [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/mbthc9.png[/img] [b]Prayer[/b] •Won't start working on until all non-combat skills are finished. [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/2qu17cw.png[/img] [b]Mining[/b] •Emptying and refilling rocks •All ores can be mined •Correct pickaxe finding and animations •Prospecting [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/ny5q8h.png[/img] [b]Smithing[/b] • All bars can be made • All bars can be smithed • All equipment can be produced • Correct animations, interfaces and objects used [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/ckvgp.png[/img] [b]Fishing[/b] • All fish can be caught • Correct item requirements • Fishing spots located all around the world • Correct animations • Moving fishing locations [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/2ld9edk.png[/img] [b]Cooking[/b] • All fish can be cooked • All meats can be cooked • Grinding wheat into flour • Pies • Pizza • Stew • Misc. cooking recepies • Correct burning formula • Cooking gauntlets • Lumbridge cooking range bonus • Correct animation and timing used [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/21j6arq.png[/img] [b]Woodcutting[/b] • Stumps and regrowing trees • Correct hatchet finding • Correct hatchet animations • All trees cut able • Correct fell chance algorithms [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2cz2geh.png[/img] [b]Firemaking[/b] • All logs light able • Adding and depleting of lightened logs • Ashes appear after logs burn out • Correct animations • Clipped [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/fbfgjc.png[/img] [b]Agility[/b] • Gnome, Wilderness, Pyramid and Brimhaven courses usable • All obstacles • Correct animations used [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/9ru1i0.png[/img] [b]Herblore[/b] • Correct animations • Herb Identifying • All potions can be made • Correct first and secondary ingredients • Weapon Poisoning • Can pour doses into other potions (must be the same potion) [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/dfhes3.jpg[/img] [b]Thieving[/b] •NPC thievery working with correct stunning formula •Can thieve from stalls and can get caught by surrounding guards •Correct animations and graphics used [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/96ksqa.jpg[/img] [b]Crafting[/b] • under construction... [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/209k1.jpg[/img] [b]Runecrafting[/b] • Use of the Abyss • All altars working • Correct multiple crafting • Use of Pouches included • Talismans "pull" to altars • Tiaras work [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/e0gx11.jpg[/img] [b]Fletching[/b] • All logs can be fletched • Option interface for short or long bow (shafts if normal log) • Can string bows • Can make arrows [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/wanls3.jpg[/img] [b]Slayer[/b] • All slayer masters • Very easy, easy, medium, hard and very hard slayer tasks • Slayer gem working • All equipment working • Correct requirements for slayer monsters [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/soxyt0.jpg[/img] [b]Farming[/b] • Under construction... [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/b6x7qw.jpg[/img] [b]Music/Sounds[/b] • Get music/sound packets • Get music/sound playing • All areas have music • All sounds added [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/zxwsc7.jpg[/img] [b]Miscellaneous[/b] • Water fillables (using vials, buckets, jugs, etc. on water sources) • Pickables (cabbages, onions, wheat, etc.)
